

=Bio=

"Boyd is the Deputy Director of Research at EADA Business School in Barcelona and the author of 3 books: Climate Capitalism (2011), The Emergence of the Urban Entrepreneur (2016) and Post-Capitalist Entrepreneurship (2017). He also regularly publishes in peer-reviewed academic journals such as California Management Review, Journal of Business Venturing and Organization & Environment as well as mainstream outlets such as Fast Company and Shareable.  He is on the board of the Mobile World Congress D-Lab for social innovation and a Fab Cities initiative to develop a circular economy initiative throughout Europe."

